## 15. Scope Control (Very Important)

Hackathon Version Includes:

* 2 playable levels
* 1 locked branch path
* 2 endings implemented
* Portal assembly animation
* Partial symbolic system

DO NOT:

* Overbuild the glyph language
* Overdesign branching
* Build a full 3D engine

Keep it tight.

